<h1>Habit Tracker — Support</h1>
<p>If you need help or want to report an issue, email us at
<a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>.</p>

<h2>Quick help</h2>
<ul>
  <li><b>Add habit:</b> tap “+” on the main screen.</li>
  <li><b>Mark day:</b> tap the circle next to a habit.</li>
  <li><b>Statistics:</b> open the bar-chart icon.</li>
  <li><b>Export/Import:</b> “⋯” → Export/Import JSON.</li>
</ul>

